Package: ggManhattan
Type: Package
Title: Manhattan Plots with ggplot2
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Alfonso Saera Vila
Maintainer: Alfonso Saera Vila <alfonso.saera@example.com>
Description: Create Manhattan plots for genome-wide association studies (GWAS)
    using ggplot2. Features include customizable significance lines, SNP
    highlighting, automatic hiding of overlapping chromosome labels, and
    multiple significance correction methods (Bonferroni, FDR).
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    ggrepel,
    stats
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
